{{define "subject"}}Reset Your Greenlight Password{{end}}

{{define "plainBody"}}
Hello,

We received a request to reset your Greenlight password.

To reset your password, send a PUT request to /v1/users/password with the following JSON:

{"password": "your_new_password", "token": "{{.passwordResetToken}}"}

Important details:
- This token can only be used once
- It expires in 45 minutes
- If the token expires, request a new one by sending a POST request to /v1/tokens/password-reset

If you didn't request this password reset, you can safely ignore this email.

Best regards,
The Greenlight Team
{{end}}

